\begin_layout Standard
If any user's membership has expired, we can extend it by clicking the EDIT
 menu.
 Membership renewal can be done automatically or manually.
 Automatically, we can do it with the checkbox EXTEND : the membership will
 be extended for a specified period from the date of renewal.
 Manually, it can also be done by editing Expiry Date.
\end_layout

