\begin_layout Standard
This defines the types of membership.
 The type of membership controls Loan Limit (limit number of borrowed copies),
 Loan Period (the length of a loan), Reserve (whether reservations can be
 made), Reserve Limit (limit number of copies reserved), Membership Period
 (length of membership), Reborrow Limit (limits extensions), Fine each day
 (fine per day for overdues ), and Overdue Grace Period (tolerance in days
 for late returns).
\end_layout

